                  <milestone facs="#f044_z000" n="43" unit="folio_number"></milestone><br>passion, or from any <span class="addition">great </span><milestone facs="#f044_z001" unit="caret"></milestone>awakening of the <br>human conscious ness. She develops <br>purely on her own lines. She is not <br>symbolic of any age. It is the ages<br> that are her symbols<span class="deletion">, her reflections, her </span><br><span class="deletion">echoes</span>.<note rend="small">121</note>
