                  <milestone n="intentions_37"></milestone>it was not so. <span class="deletion">Neither </span><br>The vices of Tiberius could not destroy<br> that supreme civilization<span class="addition">,</span> any more than<br> the virtues of the Antonines could save<br> it. It fell for other, for <span class="deletion">greater </span><span class="addition">less interesting </span>reasons.<br> The <span class="deletion">S</span><span class="addition">s</span>ibyls and <span class="deletion">P</span><span class="addition">p</span>rophets of
